  "imagine a university student named maya who often studied at a local coffee shop. one afternoon, she connected to the caf\u00e9s free wi-fi and logged into her online shopping account using a website that still used http. a hacker sitting nearby was monitoring the network traffic. because the connection was not encrypted, the hacker could see mayas login information as it traveled across the network.": "581371b4eb48ba2902d07afd524490d0",
